1
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:29,950
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,650 --> 00:01:33,930
[Episode 35]

3
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,930
What Ms. Qin has said

4
00:01:41,930 --> 00:01:45,000
matches your investigation results
completely.

5
00:01:45,490 --> 00:01:46,039
Yes.

6
00:01:51,330 --> 00:01:53,800
Why isn't Wan speaking?

7
00:01:55,130 --> 00:01:56,090
Your Majesty,

8
00:01:56,460 --> 00:01:58,460
Princess Zhaoyu is my elder sister.

9
00:01:58,520 --> 00:02:00,050
I should avoid speaking on the matter.

10
00:02:00,050 --> 00:02:02,080
Besides, she has caused such a disaster,

11
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:04,140
I am too ashamed to face Your Majesty.

12
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,570
If Your Majesty wishes to punish someone,

13
00:02:09,570 --> 00:02:11,030
please punish me instead.

14
00:02:11,130 --> 00:02:12,550
Why would I punish you?

15
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:15,080
You have nothing to do with this matter.

16
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,960
Get up, get up.

17
00:02:16,730 --> 00:02:18,130
Thank you, Your Majesty.

18
00:02:24,210 --> 00:02:26,050
The Prince Yan Che's escape

19
00:02:26,890 --> 00:02:28,550
has nothing to do with Ms. Qin.

20
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,520
As for the fire incident,

21
00:02:30,770 --> 00:02:31,520
I...

22
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:33,770
cannot bear to blame her any further.

23
00:02:33,930 --> 00:02:35,240
However,

24
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:38,450
it would be inappropriate for Ms. Qin

25
00:02:38,450 --> 00:02:39,960
to remain in the restricted quarters.

26
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,210
Considering she was newly married

27
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:45,530
when she became implicated
in Prince Yan Che's affairs.

28
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,160
Here's what we'll do.

29
00:02:47,329 --> 00:02:48,079
I

30
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,360
graciously permit her to return

31
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,450
to the Marquis of Zhongyong's Mansion,

32
00:02:51,450 --> 00:02:53,250
to rest and recover peacefully.

33
00:02:53,290 --> 00:02:55,350
She must not leave without my decree.

34
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:58,000
And a royal physician
will attend to her daily.

35
00:02:59,610 --> 00:03:00,470
Wan.

36
00:03:01,450 --> 00:03:03,390
I show her such mercy

37
00:03:03,890 --> 00:03:05,680
partly because you and she

38
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,450
come from the same family.

39
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:08,840
However, this matter

40
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:10,360
should not be publicized

41
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,280
to avoid

42
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,800
further complications.

43
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,360
Yes.

44
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:18,170
Thank you for Your Majesty's benevolence.

45
00:03:18,170 --> 00:03:20,210
Thank you for Your Majesty's benevolence.

46
00:03:20,210 --> 00:03:21,410
Recently,

47
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,480
the Empress Dowager has been unwell.

48
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,270
When you have time,
come to the palace more often

49
00:03:25,270 --> 00:03:26,870
to keep Her Majesty company.

50
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,329
Yes.

51
00:03:31,890 --> 00:03:32,770
You may go now.

52
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,510
Your Highness, please wait a moment.

53
00:03:50,510 --> 00:03:52,510
I'll go inform them of your arrival.

54
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,420
Why were you distracted earlier?

55
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,320
I just find it strange

56
00:04:06,770 --> 00:04:09,400
that His Majesty acts so coldly
towards Yan Che.

57
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,150
He is his only legitimate son.

58
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,240
Even if he despises his lack of ambition,

59
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:17,010
he shouldn't be so indifferent
to his whereabouts.

60
00:04:17,010 --> 00:04:19,340
His Majesty could let Zhaoyu return home,

61
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:21,730
yet why does he show no affection

62
00:04:21,730 --> 00:04:23,290
toward his only legitimate son?

63
00:04:23,290 --> 00:04:26,290
His Majesty isn't necessarily
showing affection to Qin Zhaoyu,

64
00:04:26,290 --> 00:04:27,170
but rather bestowing favour on

65
00:04:27,170 --> 00:04:29,770
those officials
who once served Prince Yan Che

66
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,050
to win their loyalty

67
00:04:31,050 --> 00:04:32,240
and stabilise the court.

68
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,950
If he truly wanted stability,

69
00:04:34,170 --> 00:04:36,930
he wouldn't make a bastard like Yan Qi
the crown prince.

70
00:04:36,930 --> 00:04:39,159
His Majesty might not actually think this,

71
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:41,210
after all, there's still Sui.

72
00:04:41,550 --> 00:04:43,950
But His Majesty is cold towards Sui
as well.

73
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,380
This is truly strange.

74
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,230
His Majesty is distant and cold

75
00:04:48,230 --> 00:04:49,360
toward his own sons,

76
00:04:49,850 --> 00:04:51,490
yet only in front of Yan Li,

77
00:04:51,730 --> 00:04:53,530
does he act like a loving father.

78
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,770
According to Grandmother,

79
00:04:58,170 --> 00:05:00,170
this change happened
after Consort Jin's tragedy.

80
00:05:00,170 --> 00:05:01,040
Before that,

81
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,540
His Majesty was quite fond

82
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:03,860
of Sui as well.

83
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,760
Could Consort Jin's death

84
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,360
have changed his temperament
so drastically?

85
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,010
I rarely returned to the capital before.

86
00:05:09,010 --> 00:05:10,140
If you have such questions,

87
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:12,120
you could ask Grandmother about them.

88
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:12,950
However,

89
00:05:13,410 --> 00:05:14,210
it is true that

90
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:16,150
after Prince Jin's incident,

91
00:05:16,210 --> 00:05:19,200
His Majesty became increasingly suspicious
of Father.

92
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,800
It seems Consort Jin's death

93
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:23,080
is more complicated than we thought.

94
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,770
After we capture Yan Qi,

95
00:05:27,190 --> 00:05:29,390
I'll investigate this matter with you.

96
00:05:29,610 --> 00:05:30,810
For now, we don't know

97
00:05:30,850 --> 00:05:33,000
how far this conspiracy extends.

98
00:05:33,290 --> 00:05:34,820
While you're in the palace,

99
00:05:35,010 --> 00:05:36,270
be extremely careful.

100
00:05:36,650 --> 00:05:37,180
Alright.

101
00:05:41,650 --> 00:05:44,110
Grandmother's pulse is stable and healthy,

102
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,900
she's just not sleeping well,

103
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:48,620
which is why she feels somewhat fatigued.

104
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:51,680
Since I entered the palace as a consort
in my teens,

105
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,290
and the palace intrigues

106
00:05:54,290 --> 00:05:56,409
have never ceased.

107
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,560
It's just a fire,

108
00:06:00,170 --> 00:06:01,650
it won't frighten me.

109
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:03,560
Grandmother.

110
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:06,050
If you could follow your heart

111
00:06:06,050 --> 00:06:07,510
and make the choice again,

112
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,360
would you still be willing
to enter the palace as a consort?

113
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,160
Everyone living in this world

114
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:13,630
has their own troubles.

115
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:16,440
In my entire life,

116
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,930
there were only two times

117
00:06:18,930 --> 00:06:21,490
when I followed my own heart,

118
00:06:21,490 --> 00:06:22,420
and to this day

119
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:25,410
I still don't know
if they were right or wrong.

120
00:06:26,090 --> 00:06:28,050
But since they were my own decisions,

121
00:06:28,050 --> 00:06:29,170
I have no regrets.

122
00:06:29,650 --> 00:06:31,970
Even when we make our own decisions,

123
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:34,530
the outcome may not be

124
00:06:34,530 --> 00:06:36,170
what we truly wanted.

125
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:39,490
That, as well, is the irony of fate.

126
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,560
Take Zhaoyu for example,

127
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,290
if not for His Majesty's mercy,

128
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,960
she would likely be spending

129
00:06:45,409 --> 00:06:48,340
the rest of her life alone
in the forbidden quarters.

130
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,360
Wan.

131
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,220
Let me tell you something.

132
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:58,120
Don't get too involved in palace affairs.

133
00:06:58,530 --> 00:06:59,680
You and Chi

134
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:02,120
should live your own life
behind closed doors.

135
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,200
Your Father has

136
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:05,320
only Chi as his flesh and blood.

137
00:07:05,850 --> 00:07:08,240
Stay as far away from trouble as possible.

138
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,290
I will keep that in mind.

139
00:07:12,730 --> 00:07:14,170
Sui is playing outside.

140
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,940
Go find him.

141
00:07:16,610 --> 00:07:19,000
He's been looking forward to your visit
every day.

142
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,650
Yes.

143
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:41,940
Any news of Che?

144
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:43,470
Will His Majesty...

145
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:46,440
A young eunuch saw Prince Yan Che
leaving the palace,

146
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,360
accompanied by

147
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,360
what appeared to be Lord Zhao's men.

148
00:07:49,850 --> 00:07:51,050
His Majesty promised you

149
00:07:51,050 --> 00:07:52,850
he wouldn't harm Prince Yan Che,

150
00:07:53,010 --> 00:07:54,810
so please don't worry yourself.

151
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:57,409
Since the fire last night,

152
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,610
he hasn't come to see me once.

153
00:08:00,409 --> 00:08:01,610
He resents me

154
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:04,390
for pleading on Che's behalf, doesn't he?

155
00:08:04,970 --> 00:08:06,660
If I had known he would be

156
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,850
so cold-hearted,

157
00:08:09,530 --> 00:08:10,240
I...

158
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,210
Empress Dowager,

159
00:08:11,210 --> 00:08:13,540
His Majesty has reached the age of wisdom.

160
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,530
Managing such a vast court,

161
00:08:15,530 --> 00:08:17,240
how could he still be like before,

162
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:19,440
coming to pay respects to you every day?

163
00:08:19,970 --> 00:08:21,800
-If my Huai...
-Your Majesty.

164
00:08:24,690 --> 00:08:25,320
Alright.

165
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,710
Let's not speak of it.

166
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:28,870
Let's not.

167
00:08:36,900 --> 00:08:39,080
[Marquis of Zhongyong's Mansion]

168
00:08:38,179 --> 00:08:39,020
Father.

169
00:08:40,010 --> 00:08:42,409
His Majesty has actually allowed Yu
to return home to recover.

170
00:08:42,409 --> 00:08:43,970
What could be his intention?

171
00:08:43,970 --> 00:08:44,730
Silence!

172
00:08:45,010 --> 00:08:47,650
Yan, is Yu coming home?

173
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:50,460
Go and tidy up

174
00:08:50,490 --> 00:08:51,760
Yu's quarters.

175
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:53,700
Your Grace, when Yu returns,

176
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,230
will she still be the Crown Princess?

177
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:58,630
The deposed Crown Prince has already fled,

178
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,920
how can there still be a Crown Princess.

179
00:09:01,050 --> 00:09:02,890
My poor daughter!

180
00:09:03,410 --> 00:09:04,010
Quickly,

181
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:05,340
bring Madam back to her room.

182
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:05,980
Yes.

183
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:08,850
Madam, let's go.

184
00:09:11,970 --> 00:09:13,360
You're not so young anymore,

185
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,430
why do you still

186
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,210
lose your composure so easily?

187
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:18,110
I was just worried and confused.

188
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:19,910
But Father,

189
00:09:20,370 --> 00:09:21,410
the honour of
the Marquis of Zhongyong's Mansion

190
00:09:21,410 --> 00:09:22,840
depends entirely on the Eastern Palace.

191
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,590
Nonsense!

192
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,260
The lives of everyone in our household

193
00:09:26,260 --> 00:09:27,790
are in His Majesty's hands.

194
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:31,180
His Majesty allowing Yu to return

195
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,840
is a warning to us

196
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,770
not to get involved in this matter.

197
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,930
If we harbour any disloyalty again,

198
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:38,390
His Majesty will execute
our entire family.

199
00:09:38,470 --> 00:09:41,130
Father, are you really willing
to just sit and wait for death?

200
00:09:41,130 --> 00:09:42,170
Everyone in court knows

201
00:09:42,170 --> 00:09:43,960
you're the leader
of Crown Prince's faction,

202
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,620
and that His Majesty
will never trust you again.

203
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,800
Father,

204
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:52,960
are you just going to watch

205
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,840
as our titles

206
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:56,240
and everything we've worked for slip away?

207
00:09:56,450 --> 00:09:57,790
While there's still time,

208
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:59,340
let's immediately send a message
to the Northern Army

209
00:09:59,340 --> 00:10:00,940
and help His Highness rebel.

210
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,700
What a traitor!

211
00:10:03,850 --> 00:10:05,180
The Qin family's titles

212
00:10:05,410 --> 00:10:07,010
were all earned through
loyalty and bravery.

213
00:10:07,010 --> 00:10:07,840
Without loyalty,

214
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:10,440
how could we still stand
in the imperial court?

215
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:18,390
No matter how valuable the titles are,

216
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,720
they're not worth

217
00:10:21,450 --> 00:10:23,650
the lives of everyone in our household.

218
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,080
Sui.

219
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,410
Wan.

220
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:44,650
What's wrong?

221
00:10:44,650 --> 00:10:45,580
Are you unhappy?

222
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,880
I miss Mother.

223
00:10:50,010 --> 00:10:50,560
Come.

224
00:10:53,650 --> 00:10:54,480
Sui,

225
00:10:54,890 --> 00:10:57,080
my mom and dad

226
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,340
have also passed away.

227
00:10:59,250 --> 00:11:00,690
When I miss them,

228
00:11:00,890 --> 00:11:02,750
I talk to the stars in the sky,

229
00:11:03,290 --> 00:11:05,090
and it makes me feel much better.

230
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,770
Do you believe they've gone to heaven?

231
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,680
I do believe so.

232
00:11:10,930 --> 00:11:13,840
I don't know
if there are immortals in heaven,

233
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,480
and my mom used to
scold me and my dad

234
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,440
quite fiercely,

235
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,320
but I know

236
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:21,130
they were the people who loved me most
in this world.

237
00:11:21,130 --> 00:11:22,730
No matter where they are now,

238
00:11:23,130 --> 00:11:25,200
they would want me to be just like before,

239
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,410
safe and happy.

240
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,450
But I don't have a dad.

241
00:11:31,130 --> 00:11:32,250
I only have Father.

242
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,130
What's that?

243
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:46,050
Bring us some snacks.

244
00:11:47,130 --> 00:11:47,840
Yes.

245
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,800
Wan, do you trust me?

246
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,320
I trust you.

247
00:12:11,630 --> 00:12:12,830
Then, let me tell you.

248
00:12:12,930 --> 00:12:15,080
I was pretending

249
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,280
to not be able to speak

250
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:17,360
nor write.

251
00:12:18,950 --> 00:12:20,420
What happened?

252
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:22,010
Why did you have to pretend?

253
00:12:23,410 --> 00:12:24,900
Because I saw

254
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:27,130
Father killing Mother.

255
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:29,240
It was Father,

256
00:12:29,260 --> 00:12:30,540
not Prince Jin.

257
00:12:30,570 --> 00:12:31,980
I saw it with my own eyes.

258
00:12:32,370 --> 00:12:34,200
You were afraid
His Majesty would find out,

259
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,330
so you pretended to be simple-minded?

260
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:39,440
Father used to treat me as well as
he treats Li.

261
00:12:39,970 --> 00:12:41,210
But since that day,

262
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:43,230
when Father looks at me,

263
00:12:43,410 --> 00:12:45,270
his eyes are always dark and cold.

264
00:12:45,590 --> 00:12:47,960
Father's temper has gotten worse,

265
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:50,110
if he finds out, he will surely kill me.

266
00:12:50,250 --> 00:12:51,930
Wan, please believe me.

267
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,170
I believe you.

268
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,500
Don't worry, Sui,

269
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:57,420
Chi and I will protect you.

270
00:12:57,600 --> 00:13:00,530
Grandmother says you're the best coroner
in Zhou,

271
00:13:00,530 --> 00:13:01,990
I've told you everything,

272
00:13:02,010 --> 00:13:04,170
can you and Chi help me?

273
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:05,730
I don't want Mother and Prince Jin

274
00:13:05,730 --> 00:13:07,370
to have died in vain.

275
00:13:08,970 --> 00:13:10,160
I promise you.

276
00:13:12,410 --> 00:13:13,440
That day,

277
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:15,260
I was supposed to join my brothers

278
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:17,840
at the book appreciation banquet
in the rear garden.

279
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,630
Prince Jin promised me

280
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:21,450
that he would give me a gift,

281
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:24,170
but I don't like those adult banquets,

282
00:13:24,650 --> 00:13:26,700
so I pretended to be sick and didn't go.

283
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:31,030
Instead, I sneaked into Hanguang Hall
to look through Mother's collections.

284
00:13:31,330 --> 00:13:32,640
To my surprise,

285
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:35,250
Father and Mother returned early,

286
00:13:35,890 --> 00:13:37,950
so I quickly hid behind the curtains.

287
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:38,880
I ask you,

288
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:40,940
where did you get this book?

289
00:13:40,970 --> 00:13:42,070
What are you plotting?

290
00:13:42,070 --> 00:13:44,510
Your Majesty might as well tell me,

291
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,530
[Consort Jin]

292
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:46,870
why is Your Majesty's handwriting

293
00:13:47,050 --> 00:13:50,680
completely different from
that in the book?

294
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:52,170
Haven't I told you before?

295
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:53,820
I was once injured.

296
00:13:53,850 --> 00:13:56,330
I hurt my waist, back, and arms,

297
00:13:56,380 --> 00:13:58,780
so naturally my handwriting changed.

298
00:13:59,490 --> 00:14:01,940
I had never seen Father so angry.

299
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,820
I was so scared, I covered my ears.

300
00:14:19,130 --> 00:14:19,930
Sui.

301
00:14:20,570 --> 00:14:21,850
Prince Jin is here.

302
00:14:34,110 --> 00:14:35,950
[Prince Jin]

303
00:14:35,610 --> 00:14:37,810
Quickly, call the imperial physician.

304
00:14:45,530 --> 00:14:46,820
You know nothing,

305
00:14:46,850 --> 00:14:48,210
don't tell anyone,

306
00:14:48,650 --> 00:14:49,780
don't say anything.

307
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,060
Your Highness.

308
00:15:08,990 --> 00:15:10,240
It's all my fault.

309
00:15:10,450 --> 00:15:12,520
If I had dared to rush out then,

310
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:14,110
Mother wouldn't have died.

311
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:17,290
If I hadn't forgotten my promise
with Prince Jin,

312
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,880
he wouldn't have suffered this injustice.

313
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:21,790
Don't think like that.

314
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,320
Sui,

315
00:15:23,650 --> 00:15:24,510
remember this,

316
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:26,730
your mother's death
has nothing to do with you,

317
00:15:26,730 --> 00:15:29,180
and Prince Jin's suffering
isn't because of you either.

318
00:15:29,180 --> 00:15:30,260
I promise you,

319
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:31,930
Chi and I

320
00:15:32,050 --> 00:15:32,800
will definitely find out

321
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:34,800
why His Majesty killed your mother.

322
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,200
Thank you, Wan.

323
00:15:37,770 --> 00:15:38,530
Good child.

324
00:15:44,250 --> 00:15:45,170
Steward Duoshou,

325
00:15:44,990 --> 00:15:47,390
[Xuanji Pavilion]

326
00:15:45,550 --> 00:15:47,350
airing out chess manuals again?

327
00:15:48,250 --> 00:15:50,130
Welcome Prince Rui

328
00:15:50,130 --> 00:15:51,320
Princess Consort Rui,

329
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,840
and Prince Yan Sui.

330
00:15:53,110 --> 00:15:54,580
As Prince Rui said,

331
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:57,140
I can only do
these minor tasks now.

332
00:15:57,250 --> 00:15:59,790
May I ask what calligraphy samples
Prince Rui is looking for?

333
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:01,030
I'll just...

334
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:01,580
No need,

335
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:02,870
give me the key,

336
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:04,020
I'll go myself.

337
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:06,160
Then I'll trouble Prince Rui.

338
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:07,860
With those old bones of yours,

339
00:16:07,860 --> 00:16:09,060
you should rest well.

340
00:16:10,340 --> 00:16:12,540
Thank you for your concern, Prince Rui.

341
00:16:20,070 --> 00:16:22,530
These chess manuals are just
some beginner's guides,

342
00:16:22,530 --> 00:16:24,350
why does you need to
manage them personally?

343
00:16:24,350 --> 00:16:26,080
Princess Consort Rui may not know,

344
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,130
these few chess manuals,

345
00:16:27,130 --> 00:16:29,170
though not works of masters,

346
00:16:29,170 --> 00:16:31,570
are His Majesty's treasured possessions.

347
00:16:31,930 --> 00:16:33,130
Why would His Majesty

348
00:16:33,130 --> 00:16:34,600
like these books meant for children?

349
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:38,320
His Majesty is a genius at chess,

350
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:40,800
often saying that the essence of chess

351
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:42,960
lies in the simplest principles,

352
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:44,720
and that all variations
come from the same origin.

353
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:46,320
These beginner's books

354
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:49,650
have helped His Majesty
become nearly unbeatable.

355
00:16:50,250 --> 00:16:51,440
Could it be that His Majesty

356
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:54,800
deliberately loses to the Empress Dowager
and Grand Princess?

357
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:57,600
It must be due to
His Majesty's filial piety.

358
00:16:57,970 --> 00:17:00,450
Unfortunately, His Majesty
is now busy with state affairs,

359
00:17:00,450 --> 00:17:02,230
and has no time to study chess manuals,

360
00:17:02,230 --> 00:17:05,010
nor express himself
through calligraphy anymore.

361
00:17:05,010 --> 00:17:06,990
Since I have been assigned here,

362
00:17:07,320 --> 00:17:08,490
the Xuanji Pavilion

363
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:10,730
has not been collecting

364
00:17:10,849 --> 00:17:13,000
any of His Majesty's calligraphy works.

365
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,130
Thank you, Steward.

366
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:15,490
Please.

367
00:17:20,609 --> 00:17:21,420
Chi.

368
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,480
What is it?

369
00:17:25,369 --> 00:17:26,970
Help me get the one at the top.

370
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:28,780
The scroll up there.

371
00:17:28,780 --> 00:17:29,540
Which one?

372
00:17:29,609 --> 00:17:30,810
The one in the corner.

373
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,650
This one?

374
00:17:36,810 --> 00:17:39,040
It seems His Majesty
indeed hasn't visited for a long time.

375
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:42,300
Otherwise, the servants wouldn't dare
to be so negligent.

376
00:17:48,370 --> 00:17:49,610
This was the scroll I saw Mother hiding

377
00:17:49,610 --> 00:17:51,570
the last time I accompanied her

378
00:17:52,330 --> 00:17:53,850
to the Xuanji Pavilion.

379
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:55,090
Sui,

380
00:17:55,530 --> 00:17:56,990
do you know who wrote this?

381
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,290
Mother said

382
00:17:58,370 --> 00:18:01,230
this is Father's calligraphy
from before he ascended the throne,

383
00:18:01,230 --> 00:18:03,630
which she had found with great difficulty.

384
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:09,090
These two handwritings
are indeed identical.

385
00:18:09,090 --> 00:18:10,190
The seal on this,

386
00:18:10,410 --> 00:18:12,590
although is His Majesty's personal seal,

387
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:15,480
differs greatly from the handwriting
in His Majesty's vermilion rescript.

388
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:17,040
The handwriting on His Majesty's rescripts

389
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:18,300
is vigorous and sharp,

390
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:19,660
powerful and forceful,

391
00:18:19,810 --> 00:18:21,940
with none of this harmonious quality.

392
00:18:22,090 --> 00:18:22,890
Chi,

393
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,660
this is what I found
in Mother's calligraphy notes

394
00:18:26,660 --> 00:18:28,880
on the day she died.

395
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:31,420
Seems like

396
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:34,500
it was also written
before Father ascended the throne.

397
00:18:41,320 --> 00:18:43,050
The handwriting is identical.

398
00:18:45,170 --> 00:18:45,960
Sui,

399
00:18:46,410 --> 00:18:48,340
does His Majesty know you have this note?

400
00:18:48,340 --> 00:18:49,130
No, he doesn't.

401
00:18:49,130 --> 00:18:50,480
I've never told anyone.

402
00:18:51,450 --> 00:18:52,170
Sui,

403
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:53,680
go play over there for a while,

404
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:55,170
I need to speak with Chi.

405
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:05,960
Those pages and scrolls

406
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,470
that led to Consort Jin's death

407
00:19:07,470 --> 00:19:09,670
must have been disposed by His Majesty.

408
00:19:09,720 --> 00:19:10,850
I still need to carefully compare

409
00:19:10,850 --> 00:19:12,960
His Majesty's calligraphy
from before his ascension,

410
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:13,930
to better deduce

411
00:19:13,930 --> 00:19:16,790
the true reason why His Majesty
killed Consort Jin.

412
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:19,300
If what Sui said is true,

413
00:19:20,330 --> 00:19:21,610
then we can confirm

414
00:19:22,130 --> 00:19:23,090
that Prince Jin was framed

415
00:19:23,090 --> 00:19:24,690
for trying to cover up

416
00:19:24,890 --> 00:19:26,950
His Majesty's murder of Consort Jin.

417
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:29,400
Throughout history,

418
00:19:29,810 --> 00:19:32,890
whenever rulers disregard the law
and kill indiscriminately,

419
00:19:32,890 --> 00:19:34,950
it inevitably leads to public unrest

420
00:19:35,170 --> 00:19:36,280
and gives the disloyal

421
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:38,280
a justification to fight for the throne.

422
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:39,130
Therefore,

423
00:19:39,130 --> 00:19:40,330
throughout the ages,

424
00:19:40,370 --> 00:19:43,040
such actions have been seen
as omens of a dynasty's downfall.

425
00:19:43,040 --> 00:19:45,170
But His Majesty prides himself on
being an enlightened ruler

426
00:19:45,170 --> 00:19:47,440
and has always encouraged open criticism.

427
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:50,170
If news of him killing Consort Jin
were to spread,

428
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:52,040
it would likely cause court officials

429
00:19:52,040 --> 00:19:54,410
to impeach His Majesty
for breaking laws and moral codes,

430
00:19:54,410 --> 00:19:56,440
leading to turmoil throughout the court.

431
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,210
Therefore,

432
00:19:57,650 --> 00:19:58,760
His Majesty would certainly

433
00:19:58,760 --> 00:19:59,960
try to conceal it by all means.

434
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:02,680
Prince Jin only knew
that His Majesty killed Consort Jin,

435
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:04,140
not the reasons behind it.

436
00:20:04,930 --> 00:20:07,410
My father and he never revealed a word
about it,

437
00:20:07,410 --> 00:20:09,170
surely fearing it would cause chaos
in the palace

438
00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:10,900
and even disaster in the court.

439
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:12,810
Whoever moved Song Xiwen's carcass

440
00:20:12,810 --> 00:20:14,270
to Prince Jin's residence

441
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:16,400
must know the truth

442
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:19,090
and intends to make it public.

443
00:20:20,330 --> 00:20:21,890
I fear it's all for the throne.

444
00:20:21,890 --> 00:20:24,020
Then, the Empress must know the truth.

445
00:20:24,370 --> 00:20:25,570
To secure the throne,

446
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,480
she silenced Song Xiwen

447
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,850
to eliminate future troubles
for His Majesty.

448
00:20:29,850 --> 00:20:31,140
No wonder Yan Che

449
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:34,130
was titled Crown Prince by His Majesty
after this incident.

450
00:20:34,130 --> 00:20:35,200
The Empress and His Majesty

451
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:37,060
had already reached a concensus.

452
00:20:37,810 --> 00:20:39,340
Everything the Empress did

453
00:20:39,650 --> 00:20:40,960
was likely to ensure Yan Che

454
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:42,850
could smoothly inherit the throne.

455
00:20:42,850 --> 00:20:44,050
But she did not expect

456
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:46,200
that His Majesty hates being manipulated
the most.

457
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:48,040
Eventually, His Majesty
found an opportunity

458
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:50,240
to remove both her and her son's titles.

459
00:20:51,130 --> 00:20:52,460
How pitiful and tragic.

460
00:20:52,850 --> 00:20:54,160
After Yan Che escaped,

461
00:20:54,520 --> 00:20:56,450
what if he tries to make a comeback?

462
00:20:56,850 --> 00:20:58,580
If our suspicions are correct,

463
00:20:58,810 --> 00:20:59,890
then Yan Che

464
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:02,720
was deliberately allowed to escape
by His Majesty.

465
00:21:02,720 --> 00:21:04,960
I just hope he doesn't fall into
Prince Cheng's hands,

466
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:06,560
or his life will be in danger.

467
00:21:09,570 --> 00:21:10,680
What about Sui?

468
00:21:27,040 --> 00:21:28,190
Don't worry, Chi,

469
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,610
I didn't hear anything.

470
00:21:29,940 --> 00:21:30,940
Just like before,

471
00:21:31,540 --> 00:21:32,870
don't say a single word.

472
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:34,590
Keep playing dumb.

473
00:22:08,330 --> 00:22:10,240
Ambush! Protect His Highness!

474
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:17,340
I am Yan Che, Crown Prince of Zhou.

475
00:23:18,130 --> 00:23:19,810
How dare you!

476
00:23:19,810 --> 00:23:21,280
Crown Prince of Zhou?

477
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,890
Do you deserve that title?

478
00:23:23,890 --> 00:23:24,810
Yan Qi,

479
00:23:25,520 --> 00:23:26,880
what are you trying to do?

480
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:27,680
Brother,

481
00:23:28,650 --> 00:23:30,440
this is Mount Beimang,

482
00:23:30,930 --> 00:23:31,930
where all members of our Yan royal family

483
00:23:31,930 --> 00:23:33,930
come to their final rest.

484
00:23:34,810 --> 00:23:36,340
Prince Rui met his end here,

485
00:23:36,810 --> 00:23:37,760
and you

486
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:39,490
will too.

487
00:23:40,520 --> 00:23:42,960
Uncle died by your hand?

488
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:46,720
And now, you want to
kill your elder brother?

489
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:50,460
This place has beautiful mountains
and waters.

490
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,290
This precious spot

491
00:23:52,650 --> 00:23:54,110
is indeed perfect for you.

492
00:23:54,590 --> 00:23:55,990
Am I not being kind enough

493
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:57,680
as your younger brother?

494
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:58,570
Shameless!

495
00:23:59,040 --> 00:24:00,930
You think killing Uncle and I

496
00:24:01,090 --> 00:24:03,440
will secure you the Crown Prince position?

497
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:04,280
Delusional!

498
00:24:05,040 --> 00:24:05,810
Yan Qi!

499
00:24:05,810 --> 00:24:06,680
So talkative.

500
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:08,170
You've betrayed all morality,

501
00:24:08,170 --> 00:24:09,830
how could Father possibly...

502
00:25:26,520 --> 00:25:28,320
The deposed Crown Prince Yan Che

503
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,570
fled the palace

504
00:25:31,370 --> 00:25:34,770
and secretly contacted the Northern Army
to plot rebellion.

505
00:25:34,890 --> 00:25:36,170
Upon being captured,

506
00:25:37,040 --> 00:25:39,170
knowing he couldn't face the Emperor,

507
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:42,330
he

508
00:25:44,040 --> 00:25:45,170
took his own life

509
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:48,550
by slitting his own throat.

510
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:53,900
All hail Prince Cheng!

511
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:55,400
So what

512
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:59,200
if you're the legitimate son?

513
00:25:59,230 --> 00:26:06,630
All hail Prince Cheng!
All hail Prince Cheng!

514
00:26:32,610 --> 00:26:33,610
Empress Dowager!

515
00:26:34,170 --> 00:26:34,960
His Highness

516
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:36,370
has passed away.

517
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:16,300
My son!

518
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:19,820
I am to blame for Che's death.

519
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:24,050
I shouldn't have been so harsh on him,

520
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:27,950
nor should I have let him flee the palace.

521
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:33,400
I only wanted him to live freely.

522
00:27:36,610 --> 00:27:42,810
Now I have to bury my own child.

523
00:27:47,610 --> 00:27:48,960
Your Majesty, please restrain your grief.

524
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,360
Take care of your health.

525
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:51,480
Che

526
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:53,700
would be troubled in the afterlife.

527
00:27:53,770 --> 00:27:55,210
My son...

528
00:27:55,650 --> 00:27:58,550
My dear son!

529
00:28:08,570 --> 00:28:09,370
Father.

530
00:28:10,630 --> 00:28:12,890
Father, please don't blame yourself
too much.

531
00:28:12,890 --> 00:28:14,290
It was all my negligence.

532
00:28:14,780 --> 00:28:17,520
I failed to stop Che
from taking such a desperate path.

533
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:19,540
I am willing to bear all responsibility,

534
00:28:19,540 --> 00:28:22,270
I only ask that
you take care of yourself, Father.

535
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:25,410
How is this your concern?

536
00:28:26,170 --> 00:28:27,460
If Che

537
00:28:27,610 --> 00:28:30,720
had already decided to end his life,

538
00:28:31,080 --> 00:28:33,650
what could you have done?

539
00:28:33,810 --> 00:28:34,520
Rise.

540
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:36,730
My son...

541
00:28:36,760 --> 00:28:37,820
Thank you, Father.

542
00:28:41,740 --> 00:28:43,660
My child...

543
00:28:43,730 --> 00:28:45,410
Then I shall take my leave first

544
00:28:45,410 --> 00:28:46,870
and not disturb your rest.

545
00:28:52,610 --> 00:28:53,440
My son...

546
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,840
Prince Rui, please wait.

547
00:28:55,090 --> 00:28:56,620
I have something to report.

548
00:28:57,130 --> 00:28:58,720
That hairpin is truly beautiful.

549
00:28:58,720 --> 00:28:59,810
I've found it.

550
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:05,960
It was always meant as a gift for you.

551
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:08,810
Chi.

552
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,090
Chi.

553
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:19,000
Tell me the truth.

554
00:29:19,250 --> 00:29:20,490
Do you believe

555
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:22,240
that Che...

556
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:25,130
Took his own life?

557
00:29:26,050 --> 00:29:27,410
If Your Majesty doesn't believe it,

558
00:29:27,410 --> 00:29:29,170
then neither do I.

559
00:29:32,370 --> 00:29:33,970
Of course I don't believe it.

560
00:29:34,130 --> 00:29:36,410
Che was gentle by nature.

561
00:29:36,930 --> 00:29:38,660
If he wasn't forced by someone,

562
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:41,570
how could he take his own life?

563
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:43,280
I

564
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:45,870
command you

565
00:29:46,410 --> 00:29:47,900
and Wan

566
00:29:48,170 --> 00:29:51,090
