You actually hit me because of her.

596
00:31:21,930 --> 00:31:22,720
Feng Chenbi,

597
00:31:23,050 --> 00:31:24,610
I can spare your life,

598
00:31:25,040 --> 00:31:26,300
but I'm divorcing you.

599
00:31:27,090 --> 00:31:28,620
Go back and tell your father

600
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:29,810
that from today on,

601
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:31,960
your family should abandon

602
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,820
any thoughts of manipulating me.

603
00:31:35,130 --> 00:31:35,860
Understand?

604
00:31:40,170 --> 00:31:40,960
Prince.

605
00:31:55,140 --> 00:31:56,480
There's nothing to see here,

606
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:57,200
let's go.

607
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:01,240
Your Highness.

608
00:32:14,460 --> 00:32:15,890
Your Highness Prince Cheng,

609
00:32:15,890 --> 00:32:17,000
I, the Duke of Zhong,

610
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:18,960
am the foremost noble in the capital.

611
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:21,610
Your maternal family and mine
have been close for generations.

612
00:32:21,610 --> 00:32:23,360
We rise and fall together.

613
00:32:23,850 --> 00:32:25,810
Why cause such embarrassment?

614
00:32:26,130 --> 00:32:28,200
