615
00:32:29,060 --> 00:32:30,190
The Duke's mansion today

616
00:32:30,190 --> 00:32:31,910
could enjoy wealth and glory

617
00:32:32,510 --> 00:32:34,130
all because of what my mother and I

618
00:32:34,130 --> 00:32:35,990
have earned for you in the palace.

619
00:32:36,330 --> 00:32:38,000
I am now His Majesty's

620
