has none of the dignity
of a future empress.

625
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,000
Duke,

626
00:32:59,370 --> 00:33:01,680
if you still want future prosperity,

627
00:33:02,650 --> 00:33:04,910
then quietly accept this divorce decree

628
00:33:05,410 --> 00:33:07,410
