629
00:33:07,510 --> 00:33:09,350
If you insist on making trouble,

630
00:33:09,370 --> 00:33:11,700
it wouldn't be difficult for my household

631
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:14,520
to have a woman die of illness.

632
00:33:18,360 --> 00:33:20,290
Yan Qi, you bastard!

633
00:33:28,290 --> 00:33:29,250
Father.

634
00:33:29,570 --> 00:33:31,840
Go to the palace and ask the Noble Consort
