635
00:33:31,840 --> 00:33:32,760
Silence!

636
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:35,200
Haven't we been humiliated enough?

637
00:33:40,650 --> 00:33:41,440
Daughter,

638
00:33:41,930 --> 00:33:43,930
the Noble Consort does care for you,

639
00:33:44,280 --> 00:33:46,480
but she is Prince Cheng's mother first.

640
00:33:46,890 --> 00:33:48,520
Who do you think she'll side with?

641
00:33:48,520 --> 00:33:51,520
