by Prince Cheng?

642
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:53,940
It's your own fault for not being fertile.

643
00:33:53,940 --> 00:33:55,590
If you had gotten pregnant earlier,

644
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:58,090
that little tramp wouldn't have
gained the advantage,

645
00:33:58,090 --> 00:33:59,750
causing such embarrassment.

646
00:33:59,930 --> 00:34:03,130
Getting pregnant isn't something
I can just make happen.

647
00:34:03,850 --> 00:34:06,510
The Noble Consort may be favoured
in the palace,

648
00:34:06,610 --> 00:34:08,440
but she only has Yan Qi, doesn't she?

649
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:10,570
You know nothing about palace affairs.

650
00:34:10,570 --> 00:34:11,500
All these years,

651
00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:14,370
His Majesty has been
giving the Noble Consort beauty pills,

652
00:34:14,370 --> 00:34:16,300
supposedly to preserve her youth.

653
00:34:17,210 --> 00:34:19,770
The Noble Consort has indeed
maintained her beauty,

654
00:34:19,770 --> 00:34:22,210
but consuming too many medicinal compounds

655
00:34:22,210 --> 00:34:24,639
has made it impossible for her
to bear more children.

656
00:34:24,639 --> 00:34:28,570
Why would His Majesty prevent Her Highness
from having more children?

657
00:34:29,989 --> 00:34:31,389
You only need to remember

658
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:34,800
that royal favour has always been
as thin as paper.

659
00:34:35,330 --> 00:34:37,510
Preserving your own wealth and status

660
00:34:38,250 --> 00:34:39,560
is what matters most.

661
00:34:43,489 --> 00:34:45,600
[Morgue]

662
00:34:57,179 --> 00:34:59,110
Prince Yan Che's limbs were bound,

663
00:34:59,530 --> 00:35:01,159
yet no blood stains were formed.

664
00:35:01,159 --> 00:35:03,490
It suggests that he was bound after death.

665
00:35:04,530 --> 00:35:07,330
There are multiple bruises
on his chest and limbs.

666
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:08,890
The wound on his neck

667
00:35:08,890 --> 00:35:10,290
is the only fatal injury.

668
00:35:34,440 --> 00:35:35,770
When someone commits suicide
by slitting their throat,

669
00:35:35,770 --> 00:35:37,370
they would experience pain, fear,

670
00:35:37,370 --> 00:35:39,930
and even suffocation
when cutting the throat.

671
00:35:39,930 --> 00:35:42,000
So, their hand strength would weaken

672
00:35:42,730 --> 00:35:45,460
and the wound
would gradually become shallower.

673
00:35:46,930 --> 00:35:49,530
But Prince Yan Che's wound is uniform
in depth.

674
00:35:49,720 --> 00:35:51,410
It's clear the murderer acted swiftly

675
00:35:51,410 --> 00:35:52,820
without any hesitation,

676
00:35:52,850 --> 00:35:54,810
taking away his life with a single stroke.

677
00:35:54,810 --> 00:35:56,890
Prince Yan Che would rather live in prison

678
00:35:56,890 --> 00:35:59,120
than choose such a brutal death,

679
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:02,400
especially with such a small knife.

680
00:36:07,160 --> 00:36:08,360
What do you plan to do?

681
00:36:09,850 --> 00:36:10,890
Go with the flow.

682
00:36:11,530 --> 00:36:13,060
Follow His Majesty's will.

683
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:22,760
I have an urgent matter to report.

684
00:36:25,930 --> 00:36:27,540
Minister Li, please speak.

685
00:36:27,730 --> 00:36:30,370
Prince Yan Che's death is a matter
of state importance

686
00:36:30,370 --> 00:36:32,250
and cannot be settled with such haste

687
00:36:32,250 --> 00:36:33,960
based solely on Prince Cheng's testimony.

688
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,480
I humbly request Your Majesty

689
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,410
to have this case

690
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:38,540
thoroughly investigated
by the Court of Judicial Review.

691
00:36:38,540 --> 00:36:40,400
Li Muyun, what do you mean by this?

692
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:43,410
There were dozens of soldiers present
at the scene,

693
00:36:43,410 --> 00:36:45,340
what do you mean by "my testimony"?

694
00:36:46,080 --> 00:36:46,880
Your Majesty,

695
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,890
I am Zheng Baishi,
Prefect of the capital prefecture,

696
00:36:48,890 --> 00:36:51,020
and I support Minister Li's proposal.

697
00:36:51,210 --> 00:36:52,140
Zheng Baishi,

698
00:36:52,410 --> 00:36:54,210
are you conspiring with Li Muyun

699
00:36:54,540 --> 00:36:55,740
to falsely accuse me?

700
00:36:55,890 --> 00:36:57,810
Your Highness, you have mistaken.

701
00:36:57,810 --> 00:37:00,560
I merely agreed with Minister Li's
ruling according to the law.

702
00:37:00,560 --> 00:37:01,960
how is that conspiracy?

703
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:04,960
Prince Rui requests to have an audience.

704
00:37:05,970 --> 00:37:08,260
I have important evidence to present.

705
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:18,770
Your Majesty.

706
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,250
According to Princess Yongci's
examination,

707
00:37:21,250 --> 00:37:22,600
Prince Yan Che

708
00:37:22,640 --> 00:37:23,970
did not commit suicide,

709
00:37:24,210 --> 00:37:25,640
but had his throat cut by someone else,

710
00:37:25,640 --> 00:37:26,910
killed with a single stroke.

711
00:37:26,910 --> 00:37:27,730
Nonsense!

712
00:37:28,080 --> 00:37:29,340
Che had clearly

713
00:37:29,690 --> 00:37:31,250
took his own life with a dagger.

714
00:37:31,250 --> 00:37:32,770
Based on the wound analysis,

715
00:37:32,770 --> 00:37:33,770
the murder weapon

716
00:37:33,890 --> 00:37:35,180
was a long sword,

717
00:37:35,410 --> 00:37:37,740
not the dagger presented by Prince Cheng.

718
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:39,420
I have secretly compared

719
00:37:39,640 --> 00:37:41,250
the shape of the Prince Yan Che's wound

720
00:37:41,250 --> 00:37:43,730
with the blade of Prince Cheng's sword,

721
00:37:43,730 --> 00:37:45,160
and they match perfectly.

722
00:37:45,160 --> 00:37:46,120
Absurd!

723
00:37:46,120 --> 00:37:46,960
Utter nonsense!

724
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:47,560
Father,

725
00:37:47,590 --> 00:37:49,050
he's falsely accusing me!

726
00:37:55,720 --> 00:37:56,550
I...

727
00:37:58,340 --> 00:38:01,190
I ordered you to find Prince Yan Che.

728
00:38:01,920 --> 00:38:02,750
Why did you

729
00:38:03,730 --> 00:38:06,580
bind your brother's limbs

730
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:07,960
and slit

731
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:10,120
his throat?

732
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:10,980
Father...

733
00:38:14,410 --> 00:38:15,210
Because...

734
00:38:16,690 --> 00:38:17,520
Because he...

735
00:38:17,940 --> 00:38:19,960
Because he refused to return with me,

736
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:21,650
so I ordered him to be bound.

737
00:38:21,720 --> 00:38:22,870
Driven by his anger,

738
00:38:22,890 --> 00:38:24,450
he collided with my sword.

739
00:38:24,480 --> 00:38:25,960
Lies!

740
00:38:28,930 --> 00:38:29,730
Your Majesty!

741
00:38:30,080 --> 00:38:31,160
Prince Yan Che

742
00:38:32,040 --> 00:38:33,480
have died unjustly!

743
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:36,240
Your Majesty!

744
00:38:36,690 --> 00:38:37,420
Prince Cheng

745
00:38:37,620 --> 00:38:40,440
