751
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:54,200
The evidence of Prince Cheng's fratricide
is conclusive.

752
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:56,500
Your Majesty must not be lenient anymore!

753
00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:57,470
Your Majesty!

754
00:39:00,210 --> 00:39:01,000
Prince...

755
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:03,770
Prince Cheng, Yan Qi.

756
00:39:04,250 --> 00:39:05,180
You are truly

757
