760
00:39:11,940 --> 00:39:13,400
Court of Judicial Review,

761
00:39:13,410 --> 00:39:14,930
detain and interrogate him!

762
00:39:14,930 --> 00:39:15,690
Your Majesty is wise.

763
00:39:15,690 --> 00:39:16,890
Your Majesty is wise.

