00:39:18,040 --> 00:39:19,440
I'd like to see who dares.

765
00:39:19,440 --> 00:39:20,120
Who dares.

766
00:39:22,250 --> 00:39:23,160
All of you.

767
00:39:23,950 --> 00:39:25,280
Every single one of you.

768
00:39:31,890 --> 00:39:32,620
No.

769
00:39:39,900 --> 00:39:41,460
So it was you, Father.

770
00:39:42,620 --> 00:39:44,620
You've been deceiving me all along.

771
00:39:46,410 --> 00:39:49,340
You were the one
who ordered me to kill Prince Yan Che.

772
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:51,160
Now you blame me for fratricide?

773
00:39:51,160 --> 00:39:52,560
Blame me for fratricide?

774
00:39:53,690 --> 00:39:54,920
Why did you lie to me?

775
00:39:55,520 --> 00:39:57,290
Why did you lie to me?

776
00:39:57,640 --> 00:39:58,960
-Why did you lie to me?
