777
00:39:58,960 --> 00:39:59,960
Treason!

778
00:40:00,190 --> 00:40:01,290
From this day forward,

779
00:40:01,290 --> 00:40:03,120
Yan Qi is stripped of his royal status.

780
00:40:03,120 --> 00:40:06,250
