784
00:40:12,690 --> 00:40:13,530
Treason!

785
00:40:13,890 --> 00:40:15,120
Father!

786
00:40:15,830 --> 00:40:16,630
Your Majesty!

787
00:40:16,810 --> 00:40:17,610
Your Majesty!

788
00:40:18,980 --> 00:40:20,460
Please calm your anger, Your Majesty.

789
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:21,980
Che...

790
00:40:23,580 --> 00:40:27,450
My dear Che...

791
00:40:41,730 --> 00:40:42,400
Chi.

792
00:40:45,080 --> 00:40:46,770
How is His Majesty's condition?

793
00:40:46,770 --> 00:40:48,930
