795
00:40:50,120 --> 00:40:51,250
and needs more rest.

796
00:40:54,250 --> 00:40:54,820
Chi.

797
00:40:55,290 --> 00:40:56,480
Why don't we ask His Majesty

798
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:57,640
