815
00:41:31,540 --> 00:41:32,940
Let us in this life

816
00:41:33,330 --> 00:41:34,990
share our fortunes together,

817
00:41:35,140 --> 00:41:36,540
steadfast until the end.

818
00:41:45,290 --> 00:41:46,080
Yan Qi.

819
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:48,570
You've committed many evil deeds.

820
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:51,250
