824
00:41:57,640 --> 00:41:59,770
What are you watching for? Seize him!

825
00:42:21,720 --> 00:42:23,050
Greetings, Prince Rui.

826
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:26,210
I would appreciate
if Steward Yuan could be accommodating.

827
00:42:26,210 --> 00:42:27,420
I have a few words

828
00:42:27,630 --> 00:42:29,900
